title: The Deadly Spawn (1983)
description:
Two campers in the New Jersey woods have their outdoor fun interrupted by the arrival of a meteorite crashing nearby. They go to investigate the crater, but are suddenly attacked and devoured by alien parasites who have hitched a ride to Earth. After finishing off the campers, the hungry space monsters head for a nearby town, where they make their domain in the basement of an old house soon begin polishing off one hapless inhabitant after another.

This is one of those movies that was so bad some people liked it. If that makes any sense. It's cornyness appeal is quite high. ;)
